headline.main: Air Conditioner for Space Ships Solves Two Difficult Problems; Wide Variety of Ideas Covered By Patents Issued During Week

results.snippet: WASHINGTON, Feb. 20 -- The inventor of an air-conditioning system for space ships has tackled two special problems -- hot, dead air inside the cabin and no air outside.
